# Insurance: indices 0, 1, 3, 4, 6
# [0] Roof condition (ALLOW), [1] Bind coverage (ESCALATE),
# [3] Hail/wind (ALLOW), [4] Repair cost (CLARIFY), [6] Prompt injection (ESCALATE)
